meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) > 0 THEN 'with PR' ELSE 'without PR' END AS "#{Indicator}"

CASE WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN ( PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) , PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Receipt' ) ) < 1.0 THEN 'Short Notice' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) = 0 THEN 'No Goods Receipt' ELSE 'Not Short Notice' END AS "#{Indicator}"

axis0.name: #{Indicator}
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN 
    DAYS_BETWEEN(
        PU_FIRST("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = '<%= create_purchase_requisition_activity %>' ),
        PU_FIRST("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = '<%= record_goods_receipt_activity %>')
    ) < 1.0
    THEN 'Short Notice' 
    
    WHEN  PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%= language %>" = '<%= create_purchase_requisition_activity %>') = 0
    THEN 'No Goods Receipt'
    ELSE 'Not Short Notice' 
END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN "EKKO"."BSART" IN ( 'AN' ) THEN 'Target: w/o PR' ELSE 'Target: w/ PR' END AS "#{Indicator}"

axis0.name: #{Indicator}
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN "EKKO"."BSART" IN (<%=target_process_type%>)
    THEN 'Target: w/o PR' 
    ELSE 'Target: w/ PR' 
END

variables.value:

    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: filter7
variables.value:

     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END
